## Persona Creation Workflow

Build detailed audience personas:

- [ ] 1. Research synthesis: Draw from {{research_sources}} to understand audience
- [ ] 2. Demographic definition: Define demographics for {{persona_name}}
- [ ] 3. Psychographic mapping: Identify values, attitudes, and lifestyle
- [ ] 4. Behavioral analysis: Map media consumption, purchasing patterns
- [ ] 5. Pain point identification: Define key challenges and motivations
- [ ] 6. Journey mapping: Document awareness-to-loyalty journey

## Inputs
- Persona name: {{persona_name}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Research sources: {{research_sources}}
